phrases: Sorry to call you here out of the blue.
If it is a present from you, she would be happy no matter what you gave her.
And why would I know what a middle school girl would like, anyway?
Anything you would pick would be way better.
It would not be what she wants the most.
Kirino would be happiest getting something related to her hobby.
That is why I am asking you for help!
Are you accepting Kirino's otaku hobby?
But it is a celebration for her, so I am making an exception this time...
Also, Kirino has been talking to me a little about anime...
Ones that are not indecent, anyway.
But it is still not good enough for her.
Why do you have so many of the same ones?
It is hard to collect them all.
What do you do after you collect them?
She would not talk to me for a while after that.
I was on the verge of tears...
Those are on the top three list of things you should not ask.
That is why I want to make up for it now!
I decided to give her something related to her hobby,
so I am asking you to help me think of what would make her the most happy!
She is thinking about Kirino in her own way.
I will look into what kind of present she wants.
Are you thinking of giving me a present or something?
You made me buy stuff for you on Christmas Eve, did not you?
That was for my research, so it does not count.
Do not take that the wrong way.
And come to think of it,
you have been making passes at my friends recently.
And you have been meeting with the black one and Saori without me.
Th-They are my friends now, too!
So I can get along with them however I want!
Why are you being so picky?
So you got into a fight and could not find out from her?
More importantly, did you tell Kirino about what we did?
Hey, the restroom here is the cockpit for the Omega!
That is the Justeen Cafe for you.
I wonder what the men's side is like.
She did not find out about the anime studio incident.
We said you really wanted to see us and called us here.
What kind of cheap guy did you turn me into?!
Let us get back to the topic.
Basically, you want to know what Miss Kiririn wants, right?
I figured you guys would definitely know better than me.
Well, we were also thinking of holding a party celebrating her anime.
I am doing it because I want to.
But now that we are ready, let us search for what Miss Kiririn desires!
The first thing that comes to mind would probably be this kind of stuff.
It would not be too hard.
They do not sell them either, so there is some value to it.
But it does not feel quite right...
This seems a bit weird for what she would want the most.
Then perhaps a visual fanbook for eroge she likes?
but the requester would murder me over this.
There is no point in coming here.
She probably already has everything she wants from here.
The greatest work of art ever to grace the Earth at the hands of Man, for Y980?
Are you sure a Meruru plushie is not good enough?
It is probably the best thing we have found so far,
but I get the feeling there is something even better out there.
It is just not coming to mind.
It just has to be backwards compatible with that, right?
Something she would like, and is not indecent.
Something hard to obtain, with real value behind it.
Something like that will not just pop
Please repeat what you just said.
Kirino is a huge fan of that anime.
It does not look like something indecent.
So I was thinking, maybe a figure they do not sell would be perfect.
It is hard to get your hands on, and for people into the stuff, it is invaluable.
Goods for this anime are fine.
But I do not see how we can obtain this item that is not for sale.
It is the prize for winning a Meruru cosplay competition.
You are telling me to participate?
Well, I mean, you are a model...
And you are beautiful, and you can definitely go for first place...
How could I appear on stage wearing something as embarrassing as this?!
Do you want me to kill you, you pervert?!
Listen to everything I have to say!
And you would not look good in Meruru's outfit anyway!
I have done my research here!
This is the winner of the last one, Bridget-chan!
No matter what kind of mind-melting performance you do, you cannot win against this!
And I would not do a mind-melting performance in the first place!
This contest is all about fitting the role!
It is more about looking like the character than the impact!
And it is not like you do not have a chance.
You are definitely prettier than her.
And you are a professional model, too.
You know how to bring out the best in clothes.
You can definitely win with the right character.
It sounds like you are saying there is a character that looks like me.
Dark Witch Tanatos Eros EX Mode
She is only nude in the transformation sequence!
She is lewd enough even after the transformation sequence!
I will never wear such lecherous clothes!
I cannot think of anything she would want more than this!
Why is she acting like I am blackmailing her?!
We just need to win this contest and obtain the prize, correct?
You cannot win against this girl with any other character.
We just need an even cuter cosplay that looks more like the character than this girl.
This is my classmate, Kurusu Kanako.
I am Aragaki's manager, Akagi Kouhei.
You are not a producer or anything?
Dammit, I acted cute for nothing.
And do not call me Kanakana like you know me.
Why do not we go put your clothes on?
And she cut off her escape route!
Now then, let us head to the event!
This is like something out of brat anime crap!
Sorry, I forgot to tell you.
The contest today is actually a cosplay contest.
Why do I have to be in something stupid like that?!
I wonder where the car with your clothes has gone now...
Dang, that is a lot of people.
This is an anime for kids, right?
Why are all these adult males here?
It is proof that it is popular among all demographics maybe?
Today we have 23 girls who will be characters from Meruru on stage!
It is going to be fun!
I will be your host, Hoshino Kurara!
Well, it is no surprise she is here...
Or rather, we should have figured she would show up.
Good thing she is not going up there.
I am glad I am not participating in this...
If Kirino saw me cosplaying in that, I would die...
I think she would be really happy, though...
Now then, this is the winner's prizethe trophy!
There is only one of these in the world!
If only there were a character that looked like me!
It looks like we picked the right present for her.
But Kanako will see her if she is up there making a racket like that.
It will be a hard to explain if she sees us together.
We can meet up where we were earlier.
We have last year's winner, coming all the way from England again this year, Bridget-chan!
And what is with your hair?
For now, hide your face with that.
You do not want your school friends to know about this.
Hey, who is this person I know?
No, you should be able to tell once she comes out.
Now then, entry 21, Kanakana-chan, come on out!
She is crazy good at singing!
Wait, how does she know this song?
Hey, is not that a bit embarrassing for a girl?
When does this person I know come on?
It was not just because she is the spitting image.
What is with those gross otaku freaks?
Like I would even think of coming within a hundred feet of them.
Ka-Kanakana-chan, you cannot say something like that...
Me-Meruru turned into a dark witch!
Do not make little kids like that cry!
So, what did you think about my performance?
Oh right, how did you know that song?
Did you know about this anime?
But I do idol auditions regularly.
I practice at karaoke places too.
I can remember a song like that after hearing it once.
You looked like you were having fun singing it.
Were you just acting like it and making fun of the fans inside?
I like it when people call me cute.
I think that moe stuff is stupid, but I like the feeling of being worshipped when they go crazy over my singing and dancing.
You might make a good idol.
When do I get my clothes?!
